text: Tyler Vorpagel is an American politician. From Plymouth, Wisconsin, Vorpagel received his bachelor's degree in political science and public administration from University of Wisconsin-Green Bay. Vorpagel is a Republican and worked for Congressman Thomas Petri as a district director.Republican Assembly Campaign Committee-Tyler Vorpagel On November 4, 2014, Vorpagel was elected to the Wisconsin State Assembly.Current Election Results ==References== Category:Living people Category:People from Plymouth, Wisconsin Category:University of Wisconsin-Green Bay alumni Category:Wisconsin Republicans Category:Members of the Wisconsin State Assembly Category:21st- century American politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
